data.description: We interrupt your FRIENDS binge-watching with two incredible updates!Number 1: A $10,000 price reduction on this perfect house in an awesome neighborhood!Number 2: If you've been holding out for interest rates to fall, wait no more! The sellers FHA loan is assumable at 4.5% interest. You can't beat that!The ''Rachel'' at 1501 Pleasant Hollow Court will be there for you when the rain starts to pour. She's adorable, a total charmer, loved by all, and a real FRIEND of a home. Cruise through Avalon and see all the sights - beautiful common grounds, a tranquil lake, stunning pool, pickleball, and more - and then find the quietest little cul-de-sac. You'll know you've arrived when the very last house mutters to you, ''How you doin'?'' You're marvelous, of course, because this lot is private and spacious. Your wheels are already turning about how you're going to make this place your very own Central Park. Come on inside, we're all FRIENDS here. The living area is comfy-cozy and the perfect place for you and your ''roommates'' to live and laugh. The kitchen is well-equipped to whip up the most delicious trifles! And if you get the meat sweats, you can relax in the attached dining room or head upstairs.Pivot to the right to take in the glorious primary en-suite with its high ceilings and plentiful light. There are two more bedrooms and a well-placed laundry room on the second floor as well. Your beach-loving guests will be visiting you all the time! They'll be calling you from Myrtle Beach or Wilmington Airport to tell you, ''I got off the plane.'' Then they'll have you dining, shopping, and enjoying Southport, Oak Island, Holden Beach and more...You're not going to want to leave - you've found your ''lobster.''
